          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "The starter stack\n\nStart with a frontend, an API, one real database, and a few helpers for speed, media, jobs, and live updates.\n\n- Next.js frontend\n- tRPC or REST API\n- Postgres with Prisma\n- Redis, storage, queues, sockets",
