            "animation": "fade"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Feeds start simple\n\nFor a small app, query posts from followed users live. When reads get expensive, precompute each follower’s feed when a post is created.\n\n- For a small app, query posts from followed users live\n- When reads get expensive, precompute each follower’s feed when a post is created",
